---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
const metadata = { title: 'Privacy Policy' };
---
<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <div class="container mx-auto py-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">1. Data Collection</h2>
      <p>This website only collects necessary contact information (such as name and email) when you actively contact us (e.g., via contact form or email). No personal data is collected during general browsing.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">2. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
      <p>This website may use cookies to optimize your browsing experience. Cookies are not used to identify individuals. You can disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>This website may embed third-party services (such as Google Analytics, social sharing, etc.). Please refer to the privacy policies of those services for details on their data handling.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">4. Data Usage & Protection</h2>
      <p>Collected contact information is used only to respond to your inquiries or provide services. It will not be disclosed or sold to third parties. Reasonable security measures are in place to protect your data.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">5. Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have any privacy-related questions, please email us at terry.yao.work@gmail.com.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout> 